# Title: Suspicious X509Enrollment - Ps Script
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-12-23
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect use of X509Enrollment
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1553.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_x509enrollment.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administrative script

ScriptBlockText IN ("*X509Enrollment.CBinaryConverter*", "*884e2002-217d-11da-b2a4-000e7bbb2b09*")